Washington Unified Offers Support to Families During School Closure' + "\n
On March 13th, Washington Unified joined with schools across\u00a0the nation and closed its doors in an effort to fight the spread of COVID-19.\u00a0 Since Day 1 of\u00a0school closure, Washington Unified staff have rallied together to make sure that every member of the community knows that we are here to support each other through this difficult time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n
